a77cf7f0-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.location: 2 km outside of El Nadaar, Urzikstan
a77cf7f0-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.name: Aniyah Incursion

a81a2250-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.location: 2 km outside of El Nadaar, Urzikstan
a81a2250-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.name: Aniyah Palace

aafb4940-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.description: From the atrium and massive newsroom to the station’s balcony and nearby office buildings, this map could cater to serious CQB play through numerous tight corridors. Meanwhile, those using assault rifles, LMGs, marksman rifles, or sniper rifles can counterplay SMGs and shotguns with the use of various sightlines and the limited, yet still viable, verticality on offer.
aafb4940-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.name: Broadcast

ab3f0900-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.name: Chesire Park
ab3f0900-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.description: Take to the townhomes for long sightlines, the stores to capture objectives through intense CQB battles, or take to the side streets to take some shortcuts. If you dare, try to challenge those who may set up shop in second-story windows, phone booths, front yards, or scaffolding.

ad0b6490-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.description: Although this humble community is a beautiful one, don’t let it distract you from the battle. Use rooftops of buildings to gain the high ground against enemies sprinting from building to building below and use the splashes of footsteps on the rolling river to track down flanking players.
ad0b6490-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.name: Hovec Sawmill

adb31640-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.name: Mialstore Tank Factory
adb31640-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.description: For either skirmish size, expect a mix of indoor and outdoor combat zones with two large buildings – the eponymous tank factory and a warehouse – being the map’s central point of conflict due to sheer surface area and accessible rooftops. Other areas to explore include an abandoned workshop, skybridge, scrapyard, shipping area, and residential zone, with some parts of the map sectioned off if it is being used for 6v6 combat.

ae661290-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.name: Rammaza
ae661290-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.location: 14 km outside of El Nadaar, Urzikstan

afe73450-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.description: Every top of the boxcars and passenger car can be climbed on top of, which give superior verticality at the cost of being essentially exposed on all sides. Other objects, such as crates, containers, and even tank parts, can also be used to gain a height advantage or just be used as cover.
afe73450-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.name: Station

b02bde70-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.description: In the middle of the Urzikstan desert lies an urban city with a major construction project taking place at its center. With its citizens long evacuated, combat takes place from door-to-door as teams fight for control of the various overlooks and buildings. Prepare for a great mix of close-quarters combat and long-range sniper duels.
b02bde70-f600-11eb-ac44-bbfc5ec4ed67.name: Talsik Backlot
